@NODE library "Filter Library"


  13. Filter Library


  If you  have designed  good filters for special purposes,
  you  can send  them to  me via e-mail,  including a short
  description, for  example about  the  application you use
  them in, or special characteristics. I  will then include
  them in a  filter library and  distribute  them  together
  with  the program.  Remember to send only the  #?.FIR  or
  #?.WFIR  files,  saved by this  program, so  other people
  can modify your filters according to their needs.



  Thanks...(E-mail: harald.zottmann@t-online.de)

@ENDNODE


